### Post a new order
POST localhost:8080/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{

  "userId": 3,
  "address": "456 Elm St, Ann Arbor, MI 48109",
  "restaurantId": 6,
  "items": [
    {
      "idItem": 18,
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 29.99
    }
  ],
  "status": "CREATED"
}

### Update order
PUT localhost:8080/api/order/id/7
Content-Type: application/json

{

  "userId": 3,
  "address": "456 Elm St, Ann Arbor, MI 48109",
  "restaurantId": 6,
  "items": [
    {
      "idItem": 18,
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 29.99
    }
  ],
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

### Get order by id
GET localhost:8080/api/order/id/6
Accept: application/json

### Get orders by user id
GET localhost:8080/api/order/userId/1
Accept: application/json